{
  "stem": "27340.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They literally saw this-- the Brits never saw these people because they were on the island-- who saw this as a humanitarian operation.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they took a fairly strong anti-British stance.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it's because of that that the whole operation-- at least I think so-- it was to a large extent because of that attitude that the operation was highly successful from our point of view.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was-- felt fairly proud to be able to help some people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was-- if you looked at these sort of people, some carried babies on their back.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some were elderly people, but many of them died en route.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Fortunately, I-- I didn't have any such experiences at all.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They carried a similar sort of what we call plastic bags today, and that, that, that, that contained their worldly belongings.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were people dressed in very pathetic sort of situations.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And one of our problems-- well, my problem-- was that just as we were crossing the border, the babies would start crying, and that would possibly give our-- our position away.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were patrols there by fully-qualified frontier guards, both Belgian and French.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They had dogs with them, sniffer dogs and so on and so forth.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And occasionally, of course, we made contact.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then we would either be waved on, where they would smile at me because I exposed myself, of course, as the leader.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "These people were entirely relying on me for their safety, and so they should.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that was-- that's what I was there for.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I mean, nobody was going to shoot them, but they could have said, so far.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "No further, and get the hell back again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "On two occasions I had to use money, yes.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
